title: Rotary Grater white USA
description: The extraordinarily sharp and efficient Rotary Grater features a made in the USA stainless steel Microplane® blade. The Rotary Grater's signature Microplane Fine blade effortlessly grates hard cheese, such as Parmesan. It can also be used in chocolate and nuts for garnishing dishes at table side, and prepping ingredients for cooking and baking. An extra large hopper makes it possible to grate a generous amount of cheese and other ingredients at one time.
